cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI

The paper deals with constructing a compact representation of brain connectomes for individual fingerprinting, which involves machine learning techniques and statistical tests. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as the paper deals with brain imaging. Additionally, the paper involves statistical tests and computational techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
